{"tid":1016029,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"正妹養雞當寵物…愛到把牠紋上身、海邊共浴日光　網讚畫面超美","createTime":"2019-02-10T14:08:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-10T18:03:35.000Z","uid":212399,"like":11,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"bd1a7794da2d42f2c435ee990e565307f086d690","tid":1016029,"uid":212399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-10T14:08:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3886/d3886962.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3886%2Fd3886962.jpg&h=4bdcdc69&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲安潔會為丘卡穿上外出裝備，一起出門溜達。（圖／<a href=\"http://翻攝自yooying.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F%E7%BF%BB%E6%94%9D%E8%87%AAyooying.com&d=rjg6%2Bw4p6Mv2XY9C6AOo59lAIsOV5GGnQ0mU6qdzh4w%3D&h=e3a67a99\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">翻攝自yooying.com</a>／chookiethechook）<br />\n寵物小組／綜合報導<br />\n許多人家裡養的毛小孩多半是貓咪狗狗，更稀奇一點可能是蜥蜴、蝸牛、蛇之類的，而這位澳洲正妹養的，卻是一隻母雞，在網路上分享他們一起分享生活的各種照片，讓人印象非常深刻。（ETtoday寵物雲有IG了，快按追蹤）<br />\n安潔（Angel Muiri）住在澳洲墨爾本維多利亞，她最好的朋友是一隻雞，一年半前她從認識的獸醫那邊得知，有一隻母雞被人棄養、無家可歸，她靈機一動決定收養牠，取名為丘吉（Chookie），於是就有了現在的畫面，正妹和母雞的可愛日常。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3886/d3886963.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3886%2Fd3886963.jpg&h=8776dcf7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲丘卡是一隻很有個性的母雞。<br />\n安潔和今年3歲的丘吉，會在家裡賴在一起，丘吉蜷縮在安潔膝蓋上呼嚕，或是出門時丘吉就蹲在安潔肩膀上，沿著海灘散步，安潔說「丘吉是最可愛、最特別的寵物，還有自己的小個性，我帶牠出門時，牠會享受在我肩膀上得到的關注。」<br />\n一人一雞的畫面實在太特別，而安潔和丘吉之間的情感也甚至超越一般寵物，安潔還把丘吉的模樣刺青在她腿上，但對於是否建議其他人也養雞當寵物，安潔持保留態度「不是所有雞都這麼好相處。」<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3886/d3886959.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3886%2Fd3886959.jpg&h=2f3bfcfa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3886/d3886960.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3886%2Fd3886960.jpg&h=09f9db14&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3886/d3886961.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3886%2Fd3886961.jpg&h=c553db8a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://pets.ettoday.net/news/1374666\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpets.ettoday.net%2Fnews%2F1374666&d=rjg6%2Bw4p6Mv2XY9C6AOo59lAIsOV5GGnQ0mU6qdzh4w%3D&h=9de87dca\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://pets.ettoday.net/news/1374666</a>"},{"pid":"2e1e16f60b3659122595157ccf452ec6adfae249","tid":1016029,"uid":212399,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-10T14:09:35.000Z","msg":"隻雞好靚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"40bbf02aa84f67ef1d3da963af96af33ca57a652","tid":1016029,"uid":235994,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-10T14:10:43.000Z","msg":"都是想我地講返句&quot;正臭雞&quot;啫"},{"pid":"abc65dce3e08f14c38cc55569a62c0b485c17b0f","tid":1016029,"uid":2419,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-10T14:15:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.discuss.com.hk/t/7bd554/f/800x0/https://rs3.sinahk.net/cap/9/2018/11/14/b/b321f2506c520e5c8dbe0d6b81c95251.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.discuss.com.hk%2Ft%2F7bd554%2Ff%2F800x0%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Frs3.sinahk.net%2Fcap%2F9%2F2018%2F11%2F14%2Fb%2Fb321f2506c520e5c8dbe0d6b81c95251.jpg&h=eed6a81c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"efcd79ce20cdb5f4a5fd4582f5ca8327aa61782b","tid":1016029,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"abc65dce3e08f14c38cc55569a62c0b485c17b0f","tid":1016029,"uid":2419,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-10T14:15:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.discuss.com.hk/t/7bd554/f/800x0/https://rs3.sinahk.net/cap/9/2018/11/14/b/b321f2506c520e5c8dbe0d6b81c95251.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.discuss.com.hk%2Ft%2F7bd554%2Ff%2F800x0%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Frs3.sinahk.net%2